data.name: PublishTemplate
data.value:
SetCompressor #[COMPRESSOR_SOLID] #[COMPRESSOR] SetCompressorDictSize #[COMPRESSOR_DICTSIZE]
!define PRODUCT_NAME "#[PRODUCT_NAME]" !define PRODUCT_VERSION "#[PRODUCT_VERSION]" !define PRODUCT_PUBLISHER "DCCE" !define PRODUCT_COMPANY_NAME "#[PRODUCT_COMPANY_NAME]" !define PRODUCT_WEB_SITE "http://www.dcce.cn" !define PRODUCT_DIR_REGKEY "Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\App Paths\${PRODUCT_NAME}" !define PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY "Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\${PRODUCT_NAME}"
;-------------------------------- ;Include ;-------------------------------- !include "WinVer.nsh" !include "x64.nsh" !include "MUI2.nsh"
;-------------------------------- ;General ;-------------------------------- BrandingText "${PRODUCT_COMPANY_NAME}"
Name "${PRODUCT_NAME} v${PRODUCT_VERSION}" OutFile "#[OUTFILE]"
InstallDir "$PROGRAMFILES\${PRODUCT_NAME}" InstallDirRegKey HKLM "${PRODUCT_DIR_REGKEY}" ""
RequestExecutionLevel admin
ShowInstDetails show ShowUninstDetails show
;-------------------------------- ; MUI Settings ;-------------------------------- !define MUI_ICON "#[NSISDIR]\orange-install.ico" !define MUI_UNICON "#[NSISDIR]\orange-uninstall-self.ico" !define MUI_HEADERIMAGE !define MUI_HEADERIMAGE_BITMAP "#[LOGO]"
!define MUI_LANGDLL_REGISTRY_ROOT "HKLM" !define MUI_LANGDLL_REGISTRY_KEY "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" !define MUI_LANGDLL_REGISTRY_VALUENAME "NSIS:Language"
!define MUI_LICENSEPAGE_CHECKBOX !define MUI_ABORTWARNING
;-------------------------------- ;Pages ;-------------------------------- !insertmacro MUI_PAGE_WELCOME !insertmacro MUI_PAGE_LICENSE "#[LICENSE]" !insertmacro MUI_PAGE_DIRECTORY !insertmacro MUI_PAGE_INSTFILES !insertmacro MUI_PAGE_FINISH
!insertmacro MUI_UNPAGE_INSTFILES

;-------------------------------- ;Installer Sections ;-------------------------------- SectionGroup "系统必备" SEC_GRP_PREINSTALLED #[SEC_VC2013_X86]!define VCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\vcredist_x86.exe" #[SEC_VC2013_X86]Section /o "Microsoft Visual C++ 2013 Redistributable (x86)" SEC_VC2013_X86 #[SEC_VC2013_X86] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_VC2013_X86] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_VC2013_X86] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_VC2013_X86] #[SEC_VC2013_X86] File "/oname=${VCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\vcredist_x86.exe" #[SEC_VC2013_X86] ExecWait '"${VCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}" /passive' #[SEC_VC2013_X86] Delete "${VCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_VC2013_X86]SectionEnd
#[SEC_VC2013_X64]!define VCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\vcredist_x64.exe" #[SEC_VC2013_X64]Section /o "Microsoft Visual C++ 2013 Redistributable (x64)" SEC_VC2013_X64 #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_VC2013_X64] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_VC2013_X64] #[SEC_VC2013_X64] File "/oname=${VCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\vcredist_x64.exe" #[SEC_VC2013_X64] ExecWait '"${VCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}" /passive' #[SEC_VC2013_X64] Delete "${VCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_VC2013_X64]SectionEnd
#[SEC_OPC_X86]!define OPCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\opcredist_x86.msi" #[SEC_OPC_X86]Section /o "OPC Core Components Redistributable (x86)" SEC_OPC_X86 #[SEC_OPC_X86] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_OPC_X86] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_OPC_X86] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_OPC_X86] #[SEC_OPC_X86] File "/oname=${OPCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\opcredist_x86.msi" #[SEC_OPC_X86] ExecWait 'msiexec /qf /i "${OPCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}"' #[SEC_OPC_X86] Delete "${OPCREDIST_X86_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_OPC_X86]SectionEnd
#[SEC_OPC_X64]!define OPCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\opcredist_x64.msi" #[SEC_OPC_X64]Section /o "OPC Core Components Redistributable (x64)" SEC_OPC_X64 #[SEC_OPC_X64] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_OPC_X64] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_OPC_X64] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_OPC_X64] #[SEC_OPC_X64] File "/oname=${OPCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\opcredist_x64.msi" #[SEC_OPC_X64] ExecWait 'msiexec /qf /i "${OPCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}"' #[SEC_OPC_X64] Delete "${OPCREDIST_X64_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_OPC_X64]SectionEnd
#[SEC_DOTNETFX4]!define DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\dotNetFx40_Full_x86_x64.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]!define DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME_CHS "$TEMP\dotNetFx40LP_Full_x86_x64zh-Hans.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]Section /o "Microsoft .NET Framework 4" SEC_DOTNETFX4 #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] File "/oname=${DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\dotNetFx40_Full_x86_x64.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] File "/oname=${DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME_CHS}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\dotNetFx40LP_Full_x86_x64zh-Hans.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] ExecWait '"${DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME}" /q /norestart /ChainingPackage FullX64BootStrapper' #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] Delete "${DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] Delete "${DOTNETFX4_INSTALLER_NAME_CHS}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]SectionEnd
#[SEC_DOTNETFX2]!define DOTNETFX2_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\framework2.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]Section /o "Microsoft .NET Framework 2.0" SEC_DOTNETFX2 #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] File "/oname=${DOTNETFX2_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\framework2.exe" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] ExecWait "${DOTNETFX2_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] Delete "${DOTNETFX2_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]SectionEnd
#[SEC_OWC11]!define OWC11_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\owc11.exe" #[SEC_OWC11]Section /o "Microsoft Office 2003 Web Components" SEC_OWC11 #[SEC_OWC11] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_OWC11] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_OWC11] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_OWC11] #[SEC_OWC11] File "/oname=${OWC11_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\owc11.exe" #[SEC_OWC11] ExecWait "${OWC11_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_OWC11] Delete "${OWC11_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_OWC11]SectionEnd
#[SEC_MYSQL55]!define MYSQL_INSTALLER_NAME "$TEMP\MySql.msi" #[SEC_MYSQL55]Section /o "MySQL Database Server 5.5" SEC_MYSQL55 #[SEC_MYSQL55] SetDetailsPrint textonly #[SEC_MYSQL55] DetailPrint "正在安装 ${__SECTION__}" #[SEC_MYSQL55] SetDetailsPrint listonly #[SEC_MYSQL55] #[SEC_MYSQL55] File "/oname=${MYSQL_INSTALLER_NAME}" "#[DVIEWDIR]\Setup\MySql.msi" #[SEC_MYSQL55] ExecWait 'msiexec /qf /i "${MYSQL_INSTALLER_NAME}"' #[SEC_MYSQL55] Delete "${MYSQL_INSTALLER_NAME}" #[SEC_MYSQL55]SectionEnd SectionGroupEnd
Section "MainSection" SEC01 CreateDirectory "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}" CreateDirectory "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\Tools"
;SetOutPath "$SYSDIR" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\APRXDIST.EXE" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\opc_aeps.dll" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\opccomn_ps.dll" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\OPCDAAuto.dll" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\OPCENUM.EXE" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\opchda_ps.dll" ;File "#[SYSDIR]\opcproxy.dll" ;RegDLL "$SYSDIR\opcproxy.dll" ;RegDLL "$SYSDIR\opccomn_ps.dll" ;RegDLL "$SYSDIR\opc_aeps.dll" ;RegDLL "$SYSDIR\opchda_ps.dll" ;Exec "$SYSDIR\aprxdist.exe" ;Exec "$SYSDIR\opcenum.exe /RegServer"
SetOutPath "$INSTDIR\Data" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\..\Data\AddIns.cfg" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\..\Data\NC.cfg" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\..\Data\NCFormat.cfg"
SetOutPath "$INSTDIR\Project\" File "#[PROJECT_DIR]\*.*"
SetOutPath "$INSTDIR\Project\Output" File /r /x *.pdb /x *.vshost.exe* "#[PROJECT_OUTPUT_DIR]\*.*" #[LOCAL_IN_USE]CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\${PRODUCT_NAME}(本地).lnk" "$INSTDIR\Project\Output\DHMIRUN.exe"
File "#[DVIEWDIR]\HMI\UserControl\XY曲线\KChartXY.ocx" RegDLL "$INSTDIR\Project\Output\KChartXY.ocx"
File "#[DVIEWDIR]\HMI\UserControl\WinSock\mswinsck.ocx" RegDLL "$INSTDIR\Project\Output\mswinsck.ocx"
SetOutPath "$INSTDIR\Bin" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DXP.exe" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\living1.dll" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\WinIo32.dll" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\WinIo32.sys" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DCCEClient.ocx" RegDLL "$INSTDIR\Bin\DCCEClient.ocx" CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\Tools\DXP.lnk" "$INSTDIR\Bin\DXP.exe"
File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DBMonitor.exe" File "#[DVIEWDIR]\libmysql.dll" CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\Tools\DBMonitor.lnk" "$INSTDIR\Bin\DBMonitor.exe"
;#[OPC_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DOPCServer.exe" ;#[OPC_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DOPCAddIn.exe" ;#[OPC_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DOPCKey.dll" ;#[OPC_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\DCCEOPC.dll"
#[CAM_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\MediaDll.dll" #[CAM_SERVER_IN_USE]File "#[DVIEWDIR]\CamServer.exe"
#[NETWORK_IN_USE]SetOutPath "$INSTDIR\Bin\WebServer" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\AxInterop.DCCECLIENTLib.dll" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\Config.xml" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\HttpServer.dll" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\Interop.DCCECLIENTLib.dll" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\Interop.MSScriptControl.dll" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\ShapeRuntime.dll" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]File "#[HMIDIR]\WebServer\WebServer.exe" #[NETWORK_IN_USE]CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\${PRODUCT_NAME}(网络).lnk" "$INSTDIR\Bin\WebServer\WebServer.exe" "$\"$INSTDIR\Project\Output\&/&#[PORT]$\""
#[STARTUP]
#[REGDLL] SectionEnd
Section -AdditionalIcons SetOutPath "$INSTDIR" WriteINIStr "$INSTDIR\${PRODUCT_PUBLISHER}.url" "InternetShortcut" "URL" "${PRODUCT_WEB_SITE}"
CreateDirectory "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}" CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\${PRODUCT_COMPANY_NAME}.lnk" "$INSTDIR\${PRODUCT_PUBLISHER}.url" CreateShortCut "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}\卸载 ${PRODUCT_NAME}.lnk" "$INSTDIR\uninst.exe" SectionEnd
Section -Post WriteUninstaller "$INSTDIR\uninst.exe" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_DIR_REGKEY}" "" "$INSTDIR" ; WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "DisplayName" "$(^Name)" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "UninstallString" "$INSTDIR\uninst.exe" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "DisplayIcon" "$INSTDIR\Project\DHMIRUN.exe" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "DisplayVersion" "${PRODUCT_VERSION}" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "URLInfoAbout" "${PRODUCT_WEB_SITE}" WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "Publisher" "${PRODUCT_PUBLISHER}" SectionEnd
;-------------------------------- ;Uninstaller Section ;-------------------------------- Section "Uninstall" #[UNREGDLL]
RMDir /r "$INSTDIR" RMDir /r "$SMPROGRAMS\${PRODUCT_NAME}"
#[DELSTARTUP]
DeleteRegKey HKLM "${PRODUCT_DIR_REGKEY}"
DeleteRegKey HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}"
SetAutoClose true SectionEnd
;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;; ;Get .NET Framework version based CLR2 Function GetNetFramework2Version Push $1 Push $0 ReadRegDWORD $0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v3.5" "Install" ReadRegStr $1 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v3.5" "Version" StrCmp $0 1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion +1 ReadRegDWORD $0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v3.0" "Install" ReadRegStr $1 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v3.0" "Version" StrCmp $0 1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion +1 ReadRegDWORD $0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v2.0.50727" "Install" ReadRegStr $1 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v2.0.50727" "Version" StrCmp $0 1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion +1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion: Pop $0 Exch $1 FunctionEnd
;Get .NET Framework version based CLR4 Function GetNetFramework4Version Push $1 Push $0 ReadRegDWORD $0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v4\Full" "Install" ReadRegStr $1 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v4\Full" "Version" StrCmp $0 1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion +1 ReadRegDWORD $0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v4\Client" "Install" ReadRegStr $1 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\NET Framework Setup\NDP\v4\Client" "Version" StrCmp $0 1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion +1 KnowNetFrameworkVersion: Pop $0 Exch $1 FunctionEnd
Function GetVC2013RedistX86Version Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{5e4b593b-ca3c-429c-bc49-b51cbf46e72a}" "BundleVersion" ;12.0.30501.0 IfErrors 0 Installed
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{0f8bbc41-a65c-4ba1-af69-aacd12d13f5b}" "BundleVersion" ;12.0.21005.1 IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function GetVC2013RedistX64Version Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{1b103cea-f037-4504-81de-956057b442c3}" "BundleVersion" ;12.0.30501.0 IfErrors 0 Installed
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{3838bcad-6df2-4f08-8add-a6217bd229d6}" "BundleVersion" ;12.0.21005.1 IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function GetOPCRedistX86Version Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{40656A0A-4B04-43D7-8F68-32B55B2A156D}" "DisplayVersion" ;3.00.10501 IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function GetOPCRedistX64Version Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{725FFCF9-5D38-4249-8697-9BDB415E6B00}" "DisplayVersion" ;3.00.10501 IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function IsOWC2003Installed Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\{90120000-00A4-0804-0000-0000000FF1CE}" "DisplayVersion" ;12.0.4518.1014 IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function IsMySQLServerInstalled Push $R0
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\MySQL AB\MySQL Server 5.5" "Version" ;5.5.x IfErrors 0 Installed
ClearErrors ReadRegStr $R0 HKLM "SOFTWARE\MySQL AB\MySQL Server 5.1" "Version" ;5.1.x IfErrors 0 Installed
Installed: Exch $R0 FunctionEnd
Function CheckPreinstalled Push $R0 StrCpy $R0 "0"
;针对Windows XP SP3系统 ;安装.NET Framework 2.0 SP2 (2.2.30729) ;安装.NET Framework 4 (4.0.30319) ${If} ${IsWinXP} ${AndIf} ${AtLeastServicePack} 3 #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]Call GetNetFramework2Version #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]Pop $R1 #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]${If} $R1 < '2.2.30729' #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX2} $0 #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]${Else} #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX2} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX2] SectionSetText ${SEC_DOTNETFX2} "" #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]${EndIf} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]Call GetNetFramework4Version #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]Pop $R1 #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${If} $R1 < '4.0.30319' #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} $0 #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${Else} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetText ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} "" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${EndIf} ${EndIf}
;针对Windows 7 SP1, 系统自带.NET Framework 3.5 SP1 ;无法单独安装.NET Framework 2.0 SP2, 需要通过控制面板中“打开或关闭Windows功能”来启用 ;安装.NET Framework 4 (4.0.30319) ${If} ${IsWin7} ${AndIf} ${AtLeastServicePack} 1 #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX2} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX2]SectionSetText ${SEC_DOTNETFX2} "" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]Call GetNetFramework4Version #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]Pop $R1 #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${If} $R1 < '4.0.30319' #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} $0 #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${Else} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_DOTNETFX4] SectionSetText ${SEC_DOTNETFX4} "" #[SEC_DOTNETFX4]${EndIf} ${EndIf}
#[SEC_VC2013_X86]Call GetVC2013RedistX86Version #[SEC_VC2013_X86]Pop $R1 #[SEC_VC2013_X86]${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_VC2013_X86] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_VC2013_X86] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_VC2013_X86} $0 #[SEC_VC2013_X86] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_VC2013_X86]${Else} #[SEC_VC2013_X86] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_VC2013_X86} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_VC2013_X86] SectionSetText ${SEC_VC2013_X86} "" #[SEC_VC2013_X86]${EndIf}
#[SEC_VC2013_X64]${If} ${RunningX64} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] Call GetVC2013RedistX64Version #[SEC_VC2013_X64] Pop $R1 #[SEC_VC2013_X64] ${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_VC2013_X64] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_VC2013_X64} $0 #[SEC_VC2013_X64] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_VC2013_X64] ${Else} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_VC2013_X64} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SectionSetText ${SEC_VC2013_X64} "" #[SEC_VC2013_X64] ${EndIf} #[SEC_VC2013_X64]${Else} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_VC2013_X64} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_VC2013_X64] SectionSetText ${SEC_VC2013_X64} "" #[SEC_VC2013_X64]${EndIf}
#[SEC_OPC_X86]Call GetOPCRedistX86Version #[SEC_OPC_X86]Pop $R1 #[SEC_OPC_X86]${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_OPC_X86] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OPC_X86] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OPC_X86} $0 #[SEC_OPC_X86] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_OPC_X86]${Else} #[SEC_OPC_X86] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OPC_X86} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OPC_X86] SectionSetText ${SEC_OPC_X86} "" #[SEC_OPC_X86]${EndIf}
#[SEC_OPC_X64]${If} ${RunningX64} #[SEC_OPC_X64] Call GetOPCRedistX64Version #[SEC_OPC_X64] Pop $R1 #[SEC_OPC_X64] ${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_OPC_X64] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OPC_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OPC_X64} $0 #[SEC_OPC_X64] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_OPC_X64] ${Else} #[SEC_OPC_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OPC_X64} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OPC_X64] SectionSetText ${SEC_OPC_X64} "" #[SEC_OPC_X64] ${EndIf} #[SEC_OPC_X64]${Else} #[SEC_OPC_X64] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OPC_X64} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OPC_X64] SectionSetText ${SEC_OPC_X64} "" #[SEC_OPC_X64]${EndIf}
#[SEC_OWC11]Call IsOWC2003Installed #[SEC_OWC11]Pop $R1 #[SEC_OWC11]${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_OWC11] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OWC11] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OWC11} $0 #[SEC_OWC11] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_OWC11]${Else} #[SEC_OWC11] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_OWC11} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_OWC11] SectionSetText ${SEC_OWC11} "" #[SEC_OWC11]${EndIf}
#[SEC_MYSQL55]Call IsMySQLServerInstalled #[SEC_MYSQL55]Pop $R1 #[SEC_MYSQL55]${If} $R1 == "" #[SEC_MYSQL55] IntOp $0 ${SF_SELECTED} | ${SF_RO} #[SEC_MYSQL55] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_MYSQL55} $0 #[SEC_MYSQL55] StrCpy $R0 "1" #[SEC_MYSQL55]${Else} #[SEC_MYSQL55] SectionSetFlags ${SEC_MYSQL55} ${SF_RO} #[SEC_MYSQL55] SectionSetText ${SEC_MYSQL55} "" #[SEC_MYSQL55]${EndIf}
Exch $R0 FunctionEnd ;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
;-------------------------------- ;Install Callbacks ;-------------------------------- Var RecommendedOS Function .onInit ReadRegStr $0 HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "UninstallString" ${If} $0 != "" MessageBox MB_ICONQUESTION|MB_YESNO|MB_DEFBUTTON2 "系统需移除之前版本 ${PRODUCT_NAME} 后继续安装，确定移除之前版本？" IDNO +4 System::Call 'kernel32::GetModuleFileNameA(i 0, t .R0, i 1024) i r1' WriteRegStr HKLM "${PRODUCT_UNINST_KEY}" "InstallString" "$R0" Exec "$0" Abort ${EndIf}
${If} ${IsWinXP} ${AndIf} ${AtLeastServicePack} 3 StrCpy $RecommendedOS "1" ${EndIf} ${If} ${IsWin7} ${AndIf} ${AtLeastServicePack} 1 StrCpy $RecommendedOS "1" ${EndIf} ${If} $RecommendedOS != "1" MessageBox MB_OK|MB_ICONEXCLAMATION "推荐安装在 Windows XP SP3 或 Windows 7 SP1 系统上。" ${EndIf}
Call CheckPreinstalled Pop $R1 ${If} $R1 == "0" SectionSetText ${SEC_GRP_PREINSTALLED} "" ${EndIf}
!insertmacro MUI_LANGDLL_DISPLAY FunctionEnd
Function .onInstSuccess FunctionEnd
;-------------------------------- ;Uninstall Callbacks ;-------------------------------- Var InstallString Function un.onInit !insertmacro MUI_UNGETLANGUAGE
